    "summary": "用色彩描绘青藏高原故乡景象，感受自然之美。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s1",
      "text": "My hometown is on the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p1",
      "tr": "我的家乡在青藏高原上。",
      "g": "主系表结构 + 地点状语",
      "d": "'is on'表示位置，'the Qinghai-Tibet Plateau'是专有名词，指青藏高原。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ghXVcdBVvZdbQ4xxc4itLj.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s2",
      "text": "The geography here is amazing.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p1",
      "tr": "这里的地理环境令人惊叹。",
      "g": "主系表结构",
      "d": "'geography'指地理环境，'amazing'是形容词作表语，表示令人惊叹的。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/QdUqcnHrAomDHnHiNM24mP.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s3",
      "text": "It is famous for the world's highest mountain.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p1",
      "tr": "它因世界最高峰而闻名。",
      "g": "主系表 + 原因状语",
      "d": "'be famous for'因...而闻名，'the world's highest mountain'指珠穆朗玛峰。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/76wk7xa5hkMMLpJ9khKUjB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s4",
      "text": "But this area is also full of the most amazing colours in nature.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p1",
      "tr": "但这个地区也充满了大自然中最令人惊叹的色彩。",
      "g": "转折句 + be full of结构",
      "d": "'be full of'充满，'the most amazing'最高级形式，强调色彩的美丽。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/rgHqVJFWzJdMBeAa3kGaiC.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s5",
      "text": "The colour white meets your eyes all around.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p2",
      "tr": "白色映入你的眼帘，无处不在。",
      "g": "主谓宾 + 地点状语",
      "d": "'meet your eyes'映入眼帘，'all around'到处，表示白色无处不在。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/uiZZ9CK3WNGpz39qPKZQtP.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s6",
      "text": "The clouds are clean and soft, like our white sheep.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p2",
      "tr": "云朵洁净柔软，就像我们的白羊。",
      "g": "主系表 + 比喻",
      "d": "'clean and soft'并列形容词，'like'引出比喻，将云朵比作白羊。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/k5QcyWy6bKUkyrgfmrqYyc.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s7",
      "text": "The mountains shine brightly under the sun, like white lotus flowers.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p2",
      "tr": "山峰在阳光下闪耀，像白色的莲花。",
      "g": "主谓 + 方式状语 + 比喻",
      "d": "'shine brightly'闪耀，'under the sun'在阳光下，用莲花比喻雪山的美丽。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ubmNMrMU9GMsdzzLTPRoUS.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s8",
      "text": "The lovely blue of the sky always gives me a calm feeling.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p3",
      "tr": "天空可爱的蓝色总是给我一种平静的感觉。",
      "g": "主谓双宾语",
      "d": "'give sb sth'给某人某物，'calm feeling'平静的感觉。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/5snWg6Gs2bde4JaypAXQt9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s9",
      "text": "It is like a great sea above the plateau.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p3",
      "tr": "它就像高原上方的一片大海。",
      "g": "主系表 + 比喻 + 地点状语",
      "d": "用'sea'比喻天空的广阔，'above the plateau'在高原上方。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/eoLfKJ2XLmzXVPY2tuhpRG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s10",
      "text": "And words can't express my love for the rivers and lakes.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p3",
      "tr": "言语无法表达我对河流和湖泊的热爱。",
      "g": "主谓宾 + 否定式",
      "d": "'can't express'无法表达，'love for'对...的爱。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/W5ZM4sZWLEks39VyADBrF5.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s11",
      "text": "There are a hundred kinds of blue in the water.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p3",
      "tr": "水中有上百种蓝色。",
      "g": "There be句型",
      "d": "'a hundred kinds of'上百种，夸张手法强调蓝色的丰富多样。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ZhcsHPRE6pAsbxrCq2VgvL.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s12",
      "text": "Our grasslands, forests and fields are all green.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p4",
      "tr": "我们的草原、森林和田野都是绿色的。",
      "g": "并列主语 + 系表结构",
      "d": "三个并列主语，'all'强调全部都是绿色。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/fpwhwE3RsV8Lx5GUs5hFAV.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s13",
      "text": "That's my favourite colour.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p4",
      "tr": "那是我最喜欢的颜色。",
      "g": "主系表结构",
      "d": "'favourite'最喜欢的，表达个人偏好。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Twa64ZZjo4MReT2cQJSeJk.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s14",
      "text": "It means hope because it is the colour of life.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p4",
      "tr": "它意味着希望，因为它是生命的颜色。",
      "g": "主谓宾 + 原因状语从句",
      "d": "'because'引导原因状语从句，解释绿色象征希望的原因。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/AwKTmSvfBSuwAuPeXXo4w9.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s15",
      "text": "But green is not just the colour of nature now.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p4",
      "tr": "但现在绿色不仅仅是大自然的颜色。",
      "g": "转折句 + not just结构",
      "d": "'not just'不仅仅，暗示绿色还有其他含义。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/rkWHLApmd9gju7xjQxiDvD.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s16",
      "text": "Trains are running through the plateau.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p4",
      "tr": "火车正穿越高原。",
      "g": "现在进行时",
      "d": "'are running'现在进行时，'through'穿过，描述火车运行的状态。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/SMz5FiGBmSBBRVuwvLjWQm.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s17",
      "text": "They are this beautiful colour, too.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p4",
      "tr": "它们也是这种美丽的颜色。",
      "g": "主系表结构",
      "d": "指火车也是绿色的，呼应前文的环保主题。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/8KbAENzCyN9s5AMf2aqpnP.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s18",
      "text": "The plateau is quieter than the big cities.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p5",
      "tr": "高原比大城市更安静。",
      "g": "比较级结构",
      "d": "'quieter than'比...更安静，对比高原和城市的差异。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/FRzS8XfeBNVycXViWUtswL.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s19",
      "text": "We have fewer shops and restaurants.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p5",
      "tr": "我们的商店和餐馆更少。",
      "g": "主谓宾 + 比较级",
      "d": "'fewer'更少的，修饰可数名词，说明高原商业设施较少。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/UDddoha4Vm9Aqf8oSUaWEB.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s20",
      "text": "But we have the best presents from nature.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p5",
      "tr": "但我们拥有来自大自然最好的礼物。",
      "g": "转折句 + 最高级",
      "d": "'the best'最好的，'presents from nature'大自然的礼物，强调自然之美。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/snYJmwBDCyYaJhYadsRSUR.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s21",
      "text": "In my heart, it's better than any other place.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p5",
      "tr": "在我心中，它比任何其他地方都好。",
      "g": "比较级 + any other",
      "d": "'better than any other place'比任何其他地方都好，表达最高级含义。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/QUVbis6vGKy3vvMyCTUH3X.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u12-article-s22",
      "text": "I'm proud to say that I'm from one of the most beautiful places in the world.",
      "paragraphId": "u12-article-p5",
      "tr": "我自豪地说，我来自世界上最美丽的地方之一。",
      "g": "主系表 + 不定式 + 宾语从句",
      "d": "'be proud to do'自豪地做某事，'one of the most beautiful'最美丽的...之一。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/GAMUkEAxLVFs8rNpZWYoce.mp3"
    }
  ],
